                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/7664.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Ambassador</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-06-01T22:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 1, 1913—10 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>265. Russia has officially recognized the present Provisional Government of
                    Mexico.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Henry Lane Wilson</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
